Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,玩弄他人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是一种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让人心情舒畅的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:02.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 索性这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要把迷恋你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部变成我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:09.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算会伤害到别人也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:24.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚我现在只考虑着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知为何就是停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要别人对她的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要赢了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:40.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,否则 我会越来越空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感情不是你争我夺的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且绝对不可能靠抢夺而得到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自命清高的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们性情相合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能够顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦肯定也会喜欢上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:56.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己肤浅又自私
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,决定要和麦好好交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但无论如何只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小绘你我无法再继续利用下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我重要的 唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,利用我也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别摆出这副表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你心里有数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在总算体会到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再在放学后单独见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我做了一件再也无法挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕得不敢回头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢看你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去面对你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本该这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我至少要去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别想走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天没怎么睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学也要去图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教室太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 毕竟老师不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绘鸠同学也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以一起坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在试图用普通的方式对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干 干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在「学校」的话就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆禁止交头接耳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:50.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnSentyTEA 新蒂下午茶体\bord0\c&H959595&\fs105\frz351\frx16\fry356\pos(486,558)}被提醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs210\fnSentyTEA 新蒂下午茶体\bord0\c&H383839&\frz340.9\b0\frx12\fry354\pos(897,828)}安静点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我依赖了你 利用了你 并践踏了你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最终还将自己任性的愿望强加于你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 我应得的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,发烧的话早点跟我说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没给我说的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这么做 不停下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人知道我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又想和粟屋交往了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想引起你喜欢的人的注意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明花火这样就很有魅力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能让花火不惜做到这地步也想要得到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人嫉妒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种脆弱的一面就是花火的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻略男人什么的很简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不由得越来越想注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗浸染着的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 不管你遭到再多的玷污与伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你要装作敞开心扉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而不需要表现出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反而要永远藏起来 不然内心就会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想要让对方知道我的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情到死之前只有自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没什么不好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:09.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何我觉得她或许也会说同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她的意思是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘的话听起来隐约有种孤独感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话不就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都是孤独的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连那家伙也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 起来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮我买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么没买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是茜的学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在家庭餐厅见过的那人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙也是茜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要装作敞开心扉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然记得你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我们住的这么近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要攻略男人什么的很简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:37.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花火…那啥 告诉我你的联络方式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊但你在家庭餐厅里是和男朋友一起来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样我们下次出去玩 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的能填满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是制服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为从学校回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为JK是卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花火还真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,经常被这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这气氛真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会要接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有人这样子说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个虽然有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你和皆川老师是什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙啊 都脚踏几条船了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能成为我的所有物的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:53.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小花火和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对茜来说 这货只是众多男宠中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:04.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此这货也想和她牵扯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:10.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来这货 也想让把我纳入他的「众人」之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,惨不忍睹全无起色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 明明想胜过那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:28.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是处女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 也能喜欢上我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如说 我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:43.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只有这种眼神才不会让我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:47.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很渴望 能毫无弱点地面对着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,浇灌着此时此地的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与喜欢的人接吻是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:03.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是与对这个世界一无所知是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 因为一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我们相依相偎时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:13.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我才感觉到我是如此的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真实的情感被钥匙上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在了最深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不被人 不被任何人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,宾馆 去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不对吗 我还以为你想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很温柔地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:45.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 心情问题…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:50.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,身体舒服的话 心情也会轻易地跟上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用想着哥哥的心情与麦在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常的舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:08.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算这样中间也一定有着对麦本身的渴求的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是软弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你在考虑复杂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:26.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做舒服的事 感觉会变成笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:34.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是像你这种轻浮的人是不会懂的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 差点就感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以感情用事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在摆什么架子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不是处女的自己没自信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样你的价值也就这么点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是因为很…害…怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 慢慢来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:13.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好险 差点就被煽动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:18.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起开始习惯吧 一点点地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,演技我多少也能出卖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此我能沉迷于虚幻的自己便可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再联络啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙与我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始就把自己的价值放在高处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自尊心被填满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会被消减
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相比的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正中倩_GBK\fs50\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1330.333,190.667)}真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正中倩_GBK\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1632,384)}好萌~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,0)\fn@方正中倩_GBK\frz270\c&H000000&\b1\bord0\pos(1587,738)}色色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如他人的评价一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,籍此取回自己的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,此间相差甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的存在价值寄托在他人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就像笨蛋一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像只要把被那个人所否定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就完了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那感情是来自于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听说爸爸在小花出生后不久就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说的 那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:32.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸在哪里新组成了个家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要小花了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花什么事也没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是多喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也会渐渐地疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么喜欢也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花和哥也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花和哥哥绝对不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不可能相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:21.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,与喜欢的人接吻 我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\bord0\fs105\fn@方正卡通简体\b0\frz267.3\pos(867,528)}暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了散学典礼要开始了 移动到体育馆去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:30.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火很受欢迎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能掉以轻心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掉以轻心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做过吧 花火也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 都特意说了交往吧这样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是谁 但再不退场就很奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又被一脚踏两船了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该都差不多快消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不得不再弄一个上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 明天要早起还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻和平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是很擅长隐藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了会隐隐作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的渣女雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 最可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那种女人 绝对不是真心对麦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:02.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你一直以来都是这样直接地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让人扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦要是喜欢她到就算这样也行的地步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 并不是这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么我就不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也行的啊 你也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊真是的 别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你理想的王子殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说的话 会哭得更厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有点可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点宠着最可呢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦像这样邀请我可是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:57.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的喜欢是 即便如此也行的程度的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz351.5\pos(777,591)}今天有空？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frz350.7\frx354\fry350\pos(804,738)}没空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz347.4\pos(603,873)}挤点时间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs37.5\frx10\fry346\frz348.2\pos(399,1065)}我想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钻进被窝 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,数一下绵羊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:18.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来的时候你看 暑假就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.24,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,
